transform_sql_select: SELECT t.bill_data_str, t.bill_index_no, LAST(t.unique_invoice_id, true) OVER(ORDER BY t.bill_index_no) AS unique_invoice_id FROM (SELECT bd.bill_data_str, bd.bill_index_no, CASE WHEN bd.bill_data_str LIKE 'E%' OR bd.bill_data_str LIKE 'T%' THEN -1 WHEN bd.bill_data_str LIKE 'H%' THEN TRIM(SUBSTR(bd.bill_data_str, 12, 10)) ELSE NULL END AS unique_invoice_id FROM bill_data_vw AS bd) AS t

SELECT t.bill_data_str, t.bill_index_no, LAST(t.unique_invoice_id, true) OVER(ORDER BY t.bill_index_no) AS unique_invoice_id FROM (SELECT bd.bill_data_str, bd.bill_index_no, CASE WHEN bd.bill_data_str LIKE 'E%' OR bd.bill_data_str LIKE 'T%' THEN -1 WHEN bd.bill_data_str LIKE 'H%' THEN TRIM(SUBSTR(bd.bill_data_str, 12, 10)) ELSE NULL END AS unique_invoice_id FROM bill_data_vw AS bd) AS t
